Interface RequestAware

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MailboxManager, SubscriptionManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseMailboxManager, HBaseMailboxSessionMapperFactory, InMemoryMailboxSessionMapperFactory, JCRMailboxManager, JCRMailboxSessionMapperFactory, JCRSubscriptionManager, JPAMailboxManager, JPAMailboxSessionMapperFactory, JPASubscriptionManager, MailboxSessionMapperFactory, MaildirMailboxSessionMapperFactory, OpenJPAMailboxManager, StoreMailboxManager, StoreSubscriptionManager

    public interface RequestAware
    Implementations of this interface are aware of processing requests
